{"id":139173,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/03/简讯：美泰关闭上海芭比旗舰店/","date":"2011-03-08T20:10:37Z","modified":"2011-03-08T20:10:37Z","title":"简讯：美泰关闭上海芭比旗舰店","content":"<div>\n<p>美国美泰玩具制造公司关闭了在上海的芭比娃娃旗舰店。</p>\n<p>美泰一名发言人解释说，关闭上海旗舰店是因为公司方面要采行另一战略。</p>\n<p>这一以粉红色为主色调，楼高6层的商店两年前在上海开张时曾经引起轰动。</p>\n<p>当时由于芭比娃娃在西方销量下降，美泰希望开拓在中国的芭比娃娃市场。</p>\n<p>美泰表示，上海芭比旗舰店起到了在中国提高产品知名度的目的。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/lKCWFOyvpJlIxsNXHUzOY58IcF0/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/lKCWFOyvpJlIxsNXHUzOY58IcF0/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/lKCWFOyvpJlIxsNXHUzOY58IcF0/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/lKCWFOyvpJlIxsNXHUzOY58IcF0/1/di\"></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=YdZDESn9DUo:93TM0btX18o:mqyYa2mfVbY\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=mqyYa2mfVbY\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=YdZDESn9DUo:93TM0btX18o:PFx2F_oWK34\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=PFx2F_oWK34\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=YdZDESn9DUo:93TM0btX18o:DUWcskeyX7o\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=DUWcskeyX7o\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=YdZDESn9DUo:93TM0btX18o:clraHZBW0_I\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=clraHZBW0_I\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=YdZDESn9DUo:93TM0btX18o:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=YdZDESn9DUo:93TM0btX18o:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/YdZDESn9DUo\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p><b>要翻墙？(发邮件到Gmail):hulianwangziyouAT